  </div>
  <div>
    <h3 class="font-bold">Does Xcel Energy offer solar rebates?</h3>
    <p>Yes, Xcel Energy offers the Solar*Rewards program for Denver customers, providing upfront rebates for qualifying solar installations and ongoing bill credits through net metering. The utility also offers time-of-use rates that can maximize solar savings, rebates up to \$800 for high-efficiency AC units, up to \$1,700 for heat pumps, and additional incentives for smart thermostats and battery storage systems. These utility rebates can be combined with federal and state incentives for maximum savings.</p>
  </div>
